{"tid":364827,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網購600支電子煙　休班警涉違反《應課稅品條例》被捕","createTime":"2017-08-18T17:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T06:57:57.000Z","uid":5195,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3d8be23ebcf7d547dae9f2851bbdbf92c318275b","tid":364827,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T17:08:55.000Z","msg":"加熱式電子煙近期在日韓大熱，有休班警網購600支電子煙，涉嫌違反《應課稅品條例》，被海關拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，海關近日為打擊電子煙，正進行一連串針對網上買賣私煙行動。該名警員駐守沙田田心分區警署，加入警隊約10年，事發時休班，於荔景一間速遞公司領取電子煙貨物時，被埋伏的海關人員拘捕。他聲稱替朋友領取貨品，對事件並不知情。<br />\n<br />\n加熱式電子煙含有煙草，屬應課稅品，根據《應課稅品條例》，進口、出口、製造或搬移均須向海關申領牌照及許可證，如進口於本地銷售，則須繳付稅款。任何人士觸犯《應課稅品條例》而被定罪，最高刑罰為罰款100萬元及入獄2年。"},{"pid":"3e8f0db16707aadb149cd39b4567a2f99679f81e","tid":364827,"uid":55077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T18:08:40.000Z","msg":"連登電子煙巴打小心喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc742baf3f920477df76093bdf5ef79ab76f404","tid":364827,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T18:47:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/v19730d150.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fv19730d150.png&h=559a2664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><br />\n不要怕  , 只要信 </span></span>   <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3f2295dd6a1b37449aa523faf04770228fdcd4cf","tid":364827,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T00:05:27.000Z","msg":"邊隻"},{"pid":"4ff112c54f10d95cb8361208c9c919ce234547bb","tid":364827,"uid":41149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T00:10:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊隻</blockquote><br />\niqos"},{"pid":"5748dac87494524dad8c9abf06d1ae6623a79c7f","tid":364827,"uid":48442,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-